{
  "id": "RAW_f2579e56",
  "title": "飞书合作的第一款 AI 硬件来了，居然是个 AI 录音豆。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647679031&idx=1&sn=3ebf2f18d973951548a72c6f6e36e474",
  "date": "2026-01-19 02:26:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就在今天，飞书合作发布了他们的第一款AI硬件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">是跟安克创新一起做的一个有趣的东西。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们叫做，AI录音豆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500195365\" data-ratio=\"0.6433189655172413\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1856\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=48a11b27&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJDVsYelmNBpP3JA7PT7vZ9vH2GwhaxIf1qw9zB7BxInJtmphLJCafUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">安克做的硬件，飞书提供的软件和AI服务，他两一拍即合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对，就是这么个东西，一个小小的录音豆，除了本体之外，跟AirPods的耳机和充电盒一样，他还有个充电舱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500195330\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=48b67983&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJHgibMotlxtquQqGPQZicmgQs9ulNpFLXQqfnlhPTaY2aicUrzN8oI1ibiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">主体的AI录音豆，是右边这个小小的圆形设备，有磁力，可以夹在衣服上，也可以吸在金属上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而左边这个带凹槽的方块，就是一个磁吸充电舱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把这个AI录音豆放进</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">充电舱</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的凹槽里，就能吸上，然后充电。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我也提前了一周拿到了这个产品，然后体验了将近一周的时间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在已经成了我日常最常用的两个AI录音设备之一了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">无他，因为究极便携，以及，拥有飞书生态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">老粉都知道，我是飞书死忠粉，属于公司就长在飞书上那种。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">两年前还是免费标准版，随着业务越来越多团队越来越大，一步步升级，现在都已经氪到商业旗舰版了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"60\" data-backw=\"519\" data-imgfileid=\"500195329\" data-ratio=\"0.11560693641618497\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"519\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e2885b9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJQCOqEI6coSCteSsQvoetGbvYvH7IuTaAfS0szB9SocB4jb67C5TIqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，一个拥有飞书生态的AI录音设备，实在太香了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">讲到这里，可能很多没咋用过AI录音设备的朋友，可能就要问了，AI录音硬件，到底能干个啥，这玩意，到底是不是智商税。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先简单给大家说说，AI录音设备，到底有啥用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个类型的鼻祖，其实是一个非常著名的产品，也是我2025年的年度硬件产品，Plaud。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5009259259259259\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=185cc24e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpqHoX0FUC9GfC3OfyvWguJhblQ7kFeFTnD3Dqze5FIecicJJas4icmGibiacB6rxEuI0xqpjfIwR8SeQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D12\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它的形态呢，就是一张薄薄的卡片，能吸在你的手机背面。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，大家之前也都习惯把AI录音硬件叫成AI录音卡。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很早很早以前，之所以做成这种形态，是因为IOS长期对第三方应用直接录制系统电话音频限制很强，所以单靠APP很难把电话两端的声音稳定录下来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以Plaud走的是硬件绕开路线，设备需要贴在手机背面，通过振动传导去听手机扬声器和机身传出的振动，再把它保存成音频，后面再做转写和总结。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">后来iPhone自己也支持通话内录音了，再加上大家发现这玩意录线下会议和谈话后用AI总结会议场景更大，于是这个需求逐渐被淡化，但是贴在手机背后的录音卡片这个形式，却一直被流传了下来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像这样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"320\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"500195332\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"568\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=34b7edcc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJAqteNbFjhnSmsFL0zXAn9OJgibASNgm7hTWOEtSBBkYRIsZcdKHpFJQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是这个形态有一个巨大的实际体验BUG。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是我的无限充电器是磁吸的，但是录音卡也是磁吸的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后就会经常出现这样的画面，我带着AI录音卡，我就没办法吸着充电，我要是拿下来让手机充电，我去跟别人开会就会经常忘了带。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500195334\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80405ecc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJadDDyxLLibkzKlmnVzCZmVUELIxoH5QxUgEcQ7xmPw3pWYNz7SSHiaWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就好像那句非常经典的话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我抱起砖头就没法抱你。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过飞书跟安克搞得这个产品，就形态还挺不一样的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">独树一帜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，你现在应该能理解，他为什么不是AI录音卡片，是AI录音豆了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你把它从</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">充电舱</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上拿下来以后，就是一个完美的小小的录音豆。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它背后是一个磁吸垫片，你可以把它夹在衣领上，袖口上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"535\" data-imgfileid=\"500195337\" data-ratio=\"0.7524613220815752\" data-width=\"711\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"711\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5af7f33d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJNPtNjdOrVK6menH7VicZcpGc301dIJVM5mUKuv02lXuSLFxFfMWoR0A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也可以把它贴在任何金属区域，比如手机背板，手表，保温杯，甚至是便携式氧气瓶上。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJh7BHUqkzjrkNAqRrFzsmrZibfNKNicib6RA1W7KWUPsQZ31yYQaacjGsQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"3024\" data-cropy1=\"931.2664359861592\" data-cropy2=\"3233.2733564013843\" data-height=\"4032\" data-imgfileid=\"500195338\" data-ratio=\"0.76015625\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 440px;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" data-width=\"3024\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb94afe5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJhXOtBjiaGrqtVwPhdn2ytIg0B8eiabJ9IHB04QGBoDwJlylIF0QHQrKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">非常方便。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且相当小巧，放在手上给你们直观看一下，基本上跟旧版的一元硬币差不多。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJ93ZBtx5PcoBGHloSWbOSNg05qFtJjib5uaImhKyG8mzVAJHxs4jSY7w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1280\" data-cropy1=\"110.72664359861592\" data-cropy2=\"1330.9342560553634\" data-height=\"4032\" data-imgfileid=\"500195341\" data-ratio=\"0.95390625\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 551px;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" data-width=\"3024\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7d64808&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJgXhyTlaZ85mOsRmPGia6xxt7NtwehTthQqCnLg22IRia1zhg6F40YTjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">掂量着也很轻，大概也就是两枚一元硬币的重量。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整个产品上面就一个键，按一下，会有一个震动，然后指示灯亮起，开始录音，只要指示灯亮着就说明在录。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再按一下，还是一个震动，然后指示灯灭，录音结束。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个地方的按键，是一个机械结构，是个自锁按键，按一下锁住，就会进去了，再按一下就会停止录音并且按钮会弹出来，这个地方在人机交互上就做的挺好的，即使你盲摸，也能很清楚的知道是什么状态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">交互上比我之前每次打开飞书开录音，方便太多了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之前每次线下或者啥会议的我要录音，都是打开手机，进入手机首页，在下方找到飞书，打开飞书，点击右上角加号，然后点击开始录音撰写。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500195344\" data-ratio=\"1.3101160862354893\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1206\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=27a5deec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJ8X6k43fiayZ8icb40pyag0bH6wOJHeGJFibfZC9s3r33Mkr9qEFicjLTgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对比一下， 点一下就能录音的硬件，真的减少了很多体验上的摩擦。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看到这里，你可能会问，为啥非得用飞书录音，你用别的AI录音卡片不就行了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">逻辑其实特别简单，还是因为飞书生态，我们日常讲究，所有数据进飞书...</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且它的录音转写准确度，确实也是最高的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以因为软件的限制，我其实很久以前就非常期待飞书出个类似于AI录音卡片的这种硬件了，其他家AI卡片的录音和会议纪要，都是他们自己的，看完会议纪要就没了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是飞书生态，如果是你自己的办公软件的话，那其实还有一个非常重要的东西，就是飞书知识问答，我之前也写过一篇：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&amp;mid=2647671419&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8a8c285b059257b9df128b8bc8402726&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"现在，你终于可以用飞书搭自己的AI知识库了。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在，你终于可以用飞书搭自己的AI知识库了。</span></a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是这个：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500195345\" data-ratio=\"0.46697566628041715\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"863\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=42f24a1f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJoFvevfCSIQEGoHnpMcm8vCfSiaZU7ARK7Q1NuoZOeFn9OpRNiaUtY6AQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们强调数据AI化，强调企业AI化，其实有一个很重要的东西，就是数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果我用其他的AI录音卡片，那录音、AI分析、AI出一个逐字稿和会议纪要，就没了，这个路径，其实就结束了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是对于飞书企业用户来说，录音、AI分析、AI出一个逐字稿和会议纪要之后，这个东西直接作为数据，进到知识库里，未来任何时候，我可能忘了某个问题的答案，但是以前某个会我记得开会聊过，或者我跟同事也说过，那我们就可以直接飞书知识问答，直接提问，你就可以得到，准确的回答了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以一个AI录音豆，说实话，对飞书用户的加持，在数据层面上，还是优秀非常多。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当你按照指示扫码绑定飞书之后，就可以在飞书APP的消息框里看到这个AI录音豆了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3689064558629776\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"759\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 213px;\" data-width=\"759\" data-height=\"1465\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/OjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJcxgygBuVMLBI2ZnT1M8Nzl1UoOWVa9HtFnYm6a0dIVaMH8aIwtlotg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"759\" data-cropy1=\"77.4757785467128\" data-cropy2=\"357.1764705882353\" data-imgfileid=\"500195346\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a8d18c03&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJMhmXbz8ibULxkCgr8goMNOurAzSqF5ibu8IVXia41USV83kx1PECcc7fw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再点进这个消息框，就能看到录音豆和</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">充电舱</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的剩余电量，还可以从左下角的文件同步记录里看到录音的同步情况。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">实测下来，AI录音豆自己单独的，大概能连续不断的录7~8个小时。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而如果连上</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">充电舱</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的话，按照</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">充电舱</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">320毫安的电量换算，大概能连续录32个小时。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">录音结束后是自动同步到云端的，如果对同步速度有要求，可以开一个快速传输，六七个小时的录音，传过来大概需要三分钟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.062664907651715\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1516\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195350\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7274662b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJVm9mJmaBo7bibia0kx6c5mRDFnfIoTGxzEWNZnmVCibq3pRibeHQkmSewA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">传输完成之后，就是飞书软件的主场了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我当时也听了一下录音的质量，这个AI录音豆，在底噪抑制上甚至要比鼻祖Plaud还要好上一点，这就会显得人声会更加的清晰，文字转写的时候也会更加精准。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后飞书拿着录音库库库一通总结，过个两分钟，就会有一个视频会议助手弹出来提示你，智能会议纪要已经生成好了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1787037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1174\" data-height=\"210\" data-imgfileid=\"500195351\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=79dcb6a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJaGevG0uVweLianWKic5icQiaZQh3LBMHibMa5SNSk5ZHdyS5LGSJdfSxAwg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，你就得到了一份，非常完整的可视化会议报告。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我用上周四晚上海辛和阿文的直播我们来举个例子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5731481481481482\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3c23c2f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpicGMYlHcS3tP7PHPxwar5rsbiakFLPKyBa7x3zCo4gFfWrBQ81rUBczpVSW1XoiaIE7EmaPuIQUsNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D0\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为当时涉及到了对外直播和外部嘉宾连线，所以底层会议体系其实我们用的是腾讯会议，这样对方会方便一些。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后呢，我就用AI录音豆，把全程都录了下来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为其实不止是因为这个分享非常有干货，还有个原因就是，周四他们分享完，我就得赶紧把他们的经验整理成稿子周五发，晚上差不多9点半分享完，海辛他们1点左右睡觉我需要在1点之前把稿子给他们确认，满打满算只有3个小时多一点，时间很紧迫，必须要用AI录音来进行总结和提取逐字稿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以在录了1个半小时，从AI录音豆传过去后，飞书很快的就把信息全部整理了下来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">智能会议纪要和逐字稿就全部生成完毕了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">智能会议纪要我之前也写过，我很喜欢，最开头的这个卡片总结，超级清晰，从创作流程到执行细节，面面俱到。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8603401969561325\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2234\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195352\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6d5717ca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJFMDowoic3dbxfnTicguHkcfEag6Y70xY5HpyrCDZxV2p2aA3tySccM9g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">包括不同工具和模型的对比，直接拉了一张表格，所有信息一目了然。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7039295392953929\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1476\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195354\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a43b0742&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJwSxZ7hicXibKtZVX24aM90ichbqibpQWNiaaYEJ0vuHShZYWjMv572wX74w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后就是飞书妙记提取的逐字稿，这个就是飞书的最强项了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">妙记里完美的区分了不同的说话人，点击不同人物的时间线，就能对应到相关的文字记录。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5055555555555555\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2449\" data-height=\"1239\" data-imgfileid=\"500195357\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5473bd5b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJ6vjw85zbtCE4j5pRDzwKbpONlHs8dxUZoeuXGkww7s770LiafAbaTXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个软件支持的体验，基本秒杀绝大多数的AI录音产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我就是直接把这个逐字稿，直接down了下来，扔到了GPT-5.2 Pro里，整理成了一篇直播实录，然后我自己再把所有的PPT里面的图截下来放在实录里文字对应的地方，最后逐字确认修改优化，在3个小时内就完成了整篇稿子的撰写，12点半把公众号的预览扔给了海辛和阿文进行确认。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，这篇逐字稿，也会自动的进入我前面说的，飞书知识问答，成为我们整个企业知识库的一部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如海辛和阿文的片子里有一个很美的镜头，就是小猫在水边走，水中的影子是一只孔雀。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我就可以直接问飞书知识问答，这个镜头具体是怎么实现的？然后，一分钟，我就能得到我需要的答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562929061784897\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1311\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195358\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b6f402b4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrt1hUOwJSqh63XQjTibwswJ41gQBcsZbZBfZloEE8pMiaw6moWWnyVEbic69eUlTJbKbCbsmeyvxt2A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，你录下的所有的内容，都不止是一篇普普通通的会议纪要就完事了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还能进入到飞书，与全员共享，让你所有的知识，还能在未来，继续发光发热，真正的形成闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这一整套下来，从硬件的录音，到软件的智能会议纪要，再到AI知识问答，飞书软硬件得到了非常丝滑的结合。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除此之外，还有一个很实用的功能想和你们分享，就是这个飞书硬件，它不仅支持录音，还可以配合飞书，形成实时翻译。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">用一个老黄的演讲给你们看一下实际效果：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对于那种需要听英文发布会的场景非常有用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我自己这一周，开会面试都带着这个硬件，总结一下我对于它的感受吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">首先就是，非常轻便，而且基本属于无感佩戴，走到哪带到哪，就夹在我的衣服上，也不会掉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">充电也很省心，AI录音豆自己一次能用七八个小时，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">充电舱</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">管32小时，这一周整个过程中我只给</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">充电舱</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给这个AI录音豆充过两次电。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">录音质量上，能听出对底噪做了抑制，人声效果也有强化，总体上，人声是很清晰的，一个十人的会议室里开会，无论你坐在哪个角落，它都能捕捉到你的声音。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">唯一不太满足的是，录音的传输速度还不够快，不过这也是AI录音硬件的通病了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后，说一下价格。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">硬件本身是899，差不多是AI录音硬件的平均价格，但是它有一个其他录音硬件没有的优点。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那就是，你买了这个产品之后，不仅可以获取附赠的6个月的免费会员，后续使用的时候，还能丝滑继承你账号里原本的AI额度，不用额外付费。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这一点，对于原本就是飞书企业会员的朋友，我觉得是大利好。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对于我们这种，整个公司长在飞书上的组织来说，就真的非常的香。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说实话，我已经在考虑，用公司的名义，给公司所有的小伙伴都一人配一个了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">毕竟，他真的能提效，真的能从软硬件协同的层面，给我们人类这个脆弱的记忆，叠加一层坚实的外挂大脑。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在2026年这个AI硬件的大年。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">飞书还算搞出了一个，有差异化、很有趣的产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有点意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克、水杉</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
